{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Quick Overview\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Life Wrapped} is a privacy-first audio journaling app that records voice memos, transcribes them on-device, and provides AI-powered summaries and insights.\par}
